result.name: Sun Sun Restaurant

reviews.text: Very cheap all-you-can-eat hotpot. Don't demand for quality or anything, just see it as a place for friends to gather and have a good time with minimum expenses.

The typical neighbourhood local chinese restaurnt.
Food local standard, price friendly n service good.
Nothing too fancy but can see the real face n other side of local living.
Famous for chinese hot-pot n gathering.
Food is not bad and inexpensive.

unpleasant surprise, not liking how they seat us promising 40% discount in the second person to ensure we stayed, when bringing the bill of course no discount was made and when asking him he acted as he did not say anything. Not very fresh food, dining room not very higienic conditions, most of the waiters are friendly and trying to help though. In any case I would not recommend and not going again.
Food is OK but not as hot as I like it.  Price of dim sums during afternoon tea time is reasonable but there are also competitive priced eateries offering similar fares nearby.

result.name: 新新酒家

reviews.text: 食物水平算是一般，亦不太差。價錢方面十分大眾化，雖然位處於灣仔與銅鑼灣區交界，但相比本區與其他區份的酒樓，價錢便宜可算是數一數二。
相當旺。全滿。多人吃火煱。我們二人吃片皮鴨加蒸魚的套餐。性價合理。服務好。下次再試。
我剛和我女兒去食它們的“任食火鍋”，每位$128，不收加一。抵到爛。
價錢，話平唔算好平，但以灣仔區銅鑼灣區計算，佢都算叫大衆化吧，食品中等偏好吧，今日一分錢一分貨，係好應該的。
